# {{context|transitive|obsolete|impersonal}} To fill with horror or [[disgust]]. {{defdate|Attested from the mid 16<sup>th</sup> century until the early 17<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
#* '''c. 1604''' {{w|William Shakespeare}}, ''Othello'', act 4, scene 1:
